summary:
- **Buy-Back Cancellation**: Vmoto Limited (ASX: VMT) will not proceed with the previously proposed on-market share buy-back.  
- **Reason for Cancellation**: Delisting resolution (linked to the buy-back) was not approved at the AGM on 21 May 2025.  
- **No material impact on capital structure**: No funds were deployed or raised; the buy-back was merely abandoned.  

*No other material information identified*.
